hat can take a necro to 182 in research.  I'm just not seeing a problem on Povar as far as lack of people selling these research items.  Are they expensive?  Definitely.  But so is every other tradeskill component out there now it seems.  So, I hardly see research as a larger problem than the other tradeskills as far as skill-ups are concerned.  Perhaps your server is different, though, I don't know.  What server are you on?   Seems weird to me that you have necromancers asking you to do these combines if there is no player base in this range that would hunt at this level range and thus actually need the spell (and yet still not finding any of these drop).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I'm not sure I really understand your 'raw, naked truth' paragraph.  Of course people need help to get certain things.  That's not exclusive to spells or casters even.  You can even do it without buying platinum.  Actually, if your theory were true, then no one would be able to get anything that didn't require you to buy platinum and yet people seem to get all kinds of nontradeable spells and gear.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If most of the research components always dropped from certain spots would that be an acceptable solution?  Like say Words of the Ethereal only dropped from Frogloks in Old Sebilis?  That would certainly put it more in line with some of the other tradeskills.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
